FBIS4-25624 "drchi113_u_94003" FBIS-CHI-94-113 Daily Report 12 Jun 1994 PRC MEDIA ON TAIWAN AFFAIRS Court Sentences Accused to Death Court Sentences Accused to Death OW1206070194 Beijing XINHUA in English 0648 GMT 12 Jun 94 OW1206070194 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Hangzhou, June 12 (XINHUA) -- The three murderers who killed 32 people, mainly tourists from Taiwan in the March 31 Qiandao Lake tragedy, were sentenced to death and deprived of political rights for life here today. The judgment was pronounced today by the intermediate people's court of Hangzhou city in east China's Zhejiang Province.
